race.comment: BEST COFFEE (2) finished third over 1400m at Sunshine Coast at his most recent appearance on December 14. One of the genuine hopes in the race. PUROSANGUE (1) was an impressive winner last time over 1200m at this track, leading throughout and putting 5.5 lengths on his rivals. Sure to run well again. BEE EXACT (9) gave a sight before fading late over 1200m here at his latest appearance six-and-a-half weeks ago. Has good early toe so he should be handy in the run. Shapes as one to consider. BOLD AS BRASS (3) has been freshened since finishing fifth over 1200m at Sunshine Coast. Filled a placing in a recent Sunshine Coast Inner Track trial. Winning claims on best figures.
